Find & Fix L.L.C was established in 2017 to meet the urgent need for regulating the working process of vehicle maintenance and repair workshops, and to find basic spare parts and consumables. The company is considered the first of its kind that is specialized in providing vehicle maintenance and repair services, and finding suitable spare parts for each and every automobile manufacturer and car category, as well as used spare parts from auto salvage yards.
Find & Fix L.L.C offers to transport broke down vehicles, due to mechanical failures or the occurrence of accidents, to repair workshops after consulting with workshop owners and maintenance locations through the âFind & Fix App.â Additionally, the âFind & Fix App.â enables a userâs registration either as a vehicle owner or a maintenance and repair workshop owner.
Vision Find & Fix L.L.C aspires to become one of the best companies in the Arab region and across the globe; to achieve a leadership position in vehicle maintenance and repair on the local, Arab and international levels; to offer the highest quality standards in customer services to facilitate and achieve customer goals; to provide the best solutions for vehicle maintenance and to find appropriate spare parts through the easiest and fastest way.
Mission To provide vehicle maintenance and repair services; to find spare parts for customers; to improve vehicle maintenance services and to regulate the working process of vehicle repair.
Values Provide the best means to serve customers. Quality standards. Leadership and responsibility. Development and innovation. Passion and ambition.
Objectives To occupy a distinct position locally and internationally in the field of vehicle maintenance and sale of spare parts. To deliver services to all customers in a proper way across all cities. Expansion of maintenance to reach every city and country in the world. Creation of international trade links for the sale of spare parts. To provide the best maintenance solutions and knowledge of the ways to modify vehicles to ensure formal fitment. To enable customers through the âFind & Fix App.â to follow up the maintenance and repair works carried out on their vehicles. To meet all the customer needs covering various aspects of maintenance services and sale of spare parts. To achieve full customer satisfaction of the services provided and to ensure upgrading the service level. To provide a wide array of vehicle maintenance and repair services to suit all kinds of situations starting from the transport of broke down vehicles up to completion of maintenance and exit from the workshop.
